[RADNUG](http://radnug.org) - where it all begins
=======================================================================
This code serves as a learning platform for metro style applications in Windows 8. The main focus of this code will be about learning the new features of Windows 8 and how to develop a metro style application from the ground up.

visit http://radnug.org/blog to follow along and participate!

## Getting Started
To compile the project, you'll need Visual Studio 2012. Express version should work fine.